body:
Follow up to #5186 / #5189. `prepublishOnly` ran `test`which ran the `test-browser` which tried to run saucelabs tests and that made the build fail and the release not happen.

This removes it the tests, those are handled in other GitHub Action jobs.

# PR Compliance Checks
Thank you for your Pull Request! We have run several checks on this pull request in order to make sure it's suitable for merging into this project.  The results are listed in the  following section.

## Issue Reference
In order to be considered for merging, the pull request description must refer to a  specific issue number. This is described in our Contributing Guide. We are closing this  pull request for now but you can update the pull request description and reopen the pull  request.
The check is looking for a phrase similar to: "Fixes #XYZ" or "Resolves #XYZ" where XYZ is the issue number that this PR is meant to address.
